      • gameTickAction

        public abstract void gameTickAction​(long gameTick)
        Here your hero chooses an action for the game tick. Should be something like: move and pickup items, attack, use an item, be attacked and possibly your extensions. Remember, a hero needs to only perform one of these actions per game tick. This can be a little tricky when it comes to battles!
        Parameters:
        gameTick - The gameTick currently being executed.
